# Cursor Rules – DarkBot.Net (Clean Architecture)

Desktop-бот для DarkOrbit: **WPF** + Frida bridge + Unity client.

## Слои

| Проект | Роль | Зависит от |
|--------|------|------------|
| `DarkBot.Net.Core` | Контракты (`I*Api`, `IGameFridaProbe`), модели, Options | — |
| `DarkBot.Net.Application` | Bot loop, managers, `I*AppService`, read models | Core |
| `DarkBot.Net.Infrastructure` | Frida, Unity, Login, hosted sidecars | Core, Application |
| `DarkBot.Net.Presentation` | WPF Views/ViewModels, composition root | Application, Infrastructure |

```text
Presentation → Application (I*AppService), Infrastructure (только DI)
Infrastructure → Application, Core
Application → Core
Core → (ничего)
```

## Application

- `Contracts/I*AppService` — единственный API для ViewModels
- `Models/Bot/` — UI-agnostic snapshots
- `Services/Bot|Game|Auth|Shell|Movement/` — реализации AppService
- `Managers/`, `Bot/` — bot loop, tick logic
- ❌ Нет WPF, Frida, Process

## Infrastructure

- `Game/` — FridaGameApi, launcher, lifecycle
- `Hosting/` — VerifierSidecarHostedService
- `Logging/` — Serilog host/bootstrap (`UseDarkBotSerilog`, bootstrap logger)
- Реализации `IGameClientRestartAppService`, `IGameShutdownAppService`
- ❌ Нет ViewModels, XAML

## Presentation

- ViewModels → **только** `I*AppService` + `Ui/*` контракты
- `Models/` — UI read models (map render)
- `Mapping/` — Application → Presentation DTO
- `Formatting/` — UiStrings
- `Diagnostics/` — UI-диагностика (ReactiveUI/Splat), не Serilog host
- `Ui/Config`, `Ui/Shell` — окна и навигация
- ❌ Нет прямых ссылок на Infrastructure-типы в ViewModels
- ❌ Нет `Presentation/Logging/` (Serilog — в Infrastructure)

## AppService-фасады

| Интерфейс | Назначение |
|-----------|------------|
| `ILoginAppService` | Логин, credentials, session |
| `IGameLaunchAppService` | Запуск клиента + Frida connect |
| `IBotControlAppService` | Start/pause/stop бота |
| `IBotStatusAppService` | Snapshot для UI |
| `IGameConnectionStatusAppService` | Фаза подключения |
| `IMovementAppService` | Движение корабля |
| `IAppShellAppService` | Login vs Main при старте |
| `IGameShutdownAppService` | Shutdown клиента |

## Запрещено

- ❌ ViewModel → Infrastructure / Manager / `IMovementApi`
- ❌ `Core → Infrastructure` (compile-time)
- ❌ Бизнес-логика в `Presentation/Services/`
